title: makeup, skincare & beauty 101 with MUA Cat Mignano
itunes:title: makeup, skincare & beauty 101 with MUA Cat Mignano
description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by beauty expert and makeup artist, Cat Mignano!  Cat is the gal’s go-to makeup artist and she is breaking down her tips and tricks today.  The gals chat all things makeup, skincare, and technique in today’s episode!  You might even want to take notes on this one… Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!
